### Our Pledge
We pledge to make participation in this project a harassment-free experience for everyone, regardless of age, gender, identity, experience, or background.

### Our Standards
We expect all contributors to:
- Be respectful and inclusive.  
- Use welcoming and professional language.  
- Accept constructive feedback gracefully.  
- Focus on what is best for the community.  

Unacceptable behavior includes:
- Harassment, discrimination, or personal attacks.  
- Trolling, insults, or inappropriate language.  

### Enforcement
Project maintainers have the right to remove, edit, or reject comments and contributions that violate this Code of Conduct.

### Contact
If you experience or witness unacceptable behavior, please contact the maintainers at **[your.email@example.com]**.

